<hymn_number>98</hymn_number>
<title>Indro ny Tompo Jesosy, jereo FFPM98</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Indro ny Tompo Jesosy,
 jereo,
 Tena nihafy tokoa !
 He ! fa nivesatra eso, jereo,
 Mba hamonjena anao !
 Indro Jeso, jereo Jeso.
 Izy izao dia mihevitra anao,
 Indro Jeso, jereo !

[V2]
 Indro ny Tompo Jesosy,
 jereo,
 Efa voahombo tokoa !
 He ! fa nijaly tsy meloka teo,
 Mba hamonjena anao !
 Indro Jeso, ..sns.

[V3]
 Indry ny lefo-mandoza
 jereo,
 Nenti-namely ny Tompo !
 He ! fa ny rany nirotsaka teo,
 Mba hamonjena anao !
 Indro Jeso, ..sns.</lyrics>
</song>